jmf.data.builder

Class MessageTypeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmf.data.builder.MessageTypeBuilder

  • public class MessageTypeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder for MessageType, can be reused after a build() call. The append methods will throw BufferOverflowException if there is not enough space left for the given type. Created on 8/5/15.
    Author:
    Jan Strau√ü
